high_descs: Turn left to face the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the spoon in the middle of the counter top.
Turn around, turn left at the trash can and face the stove to your left.
Put the spoon in the black pan at the far left corner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the spoon in it from the stove top.
Turn left, cross the room and hang a right at the wall to face the sink.
Put the pan with the spoon in the sink on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left towards the counter top.
Pick up the spoon from the counter top.
Turn right then head towards the stove.
Place the spoon inside the frying on the stove.
Pick up the frying pan on the stove
Turn left walk towards the wall, turn right to face the sink.
Place the frying pan inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a frying pan and a spoon inside the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your left and face the counter
Pick up a spoon from the counter
Take a step to your right so you are facing the left side of the stove
Set the spoon down in the pan on the stove
Pick up the pan with the spoon in it from off of the stove top
Turn left and then turn to face right
Put the pan with the spoon in it down in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a pan and put them both in the sink
